courses.description:
Throughout the ages real estate was one of the safest and best investments to make. It is said that investing in Real Estate is a timeless investment that protects from inflation. The 2002 – 2008 period in the World ad also Baltic states was a golden age for Real Estate developers, when almost every other person bought apartments, built houses and invested with the purpose of making money. A negative side of investment was seen when the Real Estate bubble bursted and the crisis came and because of that many got discouraged from investing.
Real Estate is one of the most profitable investments, but there are many subtleties and strategies that many Real Estate investors tend to keep quiet about. We are constantly investing in Real Estate, so we see the mistakes other investors make and that’s why we want to show you ways how to invest in Real Estate regardless of whether the economy is rising or declining.
It is said that investing in Real Estate it generates and average of 5% return. In this course we will reveal the secrets of how to make money from Real Estate with 10%, 20%, 30% or higher returns.
MAIN COURSE OBJECTIVES
To introduce what Real Estate investment is and to help you take smalls steps towards how to get started;
To help find deals, that are below the market price;
• To show different ways how to easily raise RE value;
To reveal the secrets of how to get 30% or higher return on RE investments;
To share strategies on how to create a passive cash flow exceeding you monthly income;
We put a lot of our own hands-on experience into this 7 lesson course, as well as the experience of our students and partners who developed or currently are developing Real Estate properties. We believe that this invaluable information will be interesting and useful, both for beginner investors in Real Estate as well as for people who already have experience in investment.
COURSE FORMAT AND DATE
The course is made up of 7 recorded modules (5 Basic modules and 2 PRO modules), every one of which consists of different lessons with total duration for about an hour.
The course will provide you with additional material which you will be able to download, as well as a video from our own invested properties. Depending which course option you chose, you will also get access to all of the recorded webinars. You will be able to ask questions both during live broadcasts and after them via specified e-mail address or in a closed Facebook group.

Welcome to the  Real Estate Investing course. This course is for anyone who would like to learn to understand the basic principles, strategies and secrets of real estate investing. This course is designed for beginners and advanced real estate investors. Also in this course you will learn:


- what options exist for investing in real estate;


- terms of buying and selling real estate;


- capitalization of invested funds;


- the opportunity to reliably protect funds by investing them in a reliable and stable resource, namely Real Estate;


- find out what investment options are available with minimal investments and how you can make money by choosing only the right project;


- how to register the purchase or sale of real estate;


- what taxes on personal income and what additional expenses are paid when registering or selling real estate in the primary and secondary sector.


During the course we will consider the most popular emirate for investors from all over the world and the most expensive - Dubai, you will be able to study:


- the most sought-after business districts in which real estate is actively bought and sold,


- take a detailed look at options related to investment planning,


- strategies for rapid growth and margin expansion in projects under construction,


- how to increase the investment potential of real estate;


- how to maximize resale or rental benefits,


- top UAE real estate developers who build not only in Dubai, but also around the world;


- familiarize yourself with their projects and price dynamics, and you will learn:


- the main nuances and what additional costs may arise when selling real estate in Dubai;


- at what stages auctions and closed pre-sales are held for regular investor clients,


- how to save money when selling for reinvestment through installment programs


All the important and basic principles of real estate investing in Dubai, starting with choosing, paying the down payment and signing the sales contract


“I invite you to take the course and believe that it will definitely help you learn the ins and outs of analyzing and making the right decisions, which will help you think like a professional broker, weigh the opportunities and potential of real estate, work with proven developers and their best projects for investment, acquire for yourself or build a client base and work as an investment expert who knows the ins and outs of real estate investing, recommends and earns like an expert in this field.
